---
layout: base.njk
title: Submit a Cat
---
<section class="hero">
  <p class="eyebrow">Add a new keyboard companion</p>
  <h1>Submit your cat</h1>
  <p>Every submission starts as Pending until you approve it in Airtable.</p>
</section>

<form class="submit-form" method="post" action="/api/submit" enctype="multipart/form-data">
  <label>
    Cat name
    <input type="text" name="catName" required>
  </label>

  <label>
    Your name
    <input type="text" name="humanName" required>
  </label>

  <label>
    Developer URL (GitHub, portfolio, etc.)
    <input type="url" name="devUrl" placeholder="https://">
  </label>

  <label>
    Upload photo (recommended)
    <input type="file" name="photoFile" accept="image/jpeg,image/png,image/webp,image/gif,image/avif">
  </label>

  <label>
    Or image URL
    <input type="url" name="photoUrl" placeholder="https://example.com/cat.jpg">
  </label>

  <p>Provide at least one image input. We re-host every image on Cloudinary before saving.</p>

  <label>
    Cat story
    <textarea name="story" rows="4" placeholder="Favorite editor? Weirdest keyboard habit?"></textarea>
  </label>

  <input class="hp" type="text" name="website" tabindex="-1" autocomplete="off">

  <button class="button" type="submit">Send to Airtable</button>
</form>
